#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/2.2/guides/hibernate-orm-panache.adoc:152
msgid "Once you have written your entity, here are the most common operations you will be able to perform:"
msgstr "编写实体后，可以执行以下最常见的操作："

#. type: delimited block -
#: upstream/_versions/2.2/guides/hibernate-orm-panache.adoc:160
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"// creating a person\n"
